snippet.title: LEZ | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The official gameplay trailer of LEZ, public early access very soon in August / September

Official website: https://www.lezofficial.online
Game page on Game Jolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/lez/513865

Songs used in this trailer:
- Boom Kitty - Boom Slayer (feat. Scott Foster Harris)
- meganeko - Computer Blues
- Dex Arson - Embers
- meganeko - IO
- Kioshi - Light

Thanks for all the support, Daztrax out
